{"tid":156322,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得身邊所有人都討厭自己","createTime":"2017-03-14T15:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T18:57:11.000Z","uid":19065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ced0b53e6308a0b743655f56d10dc3b2c47e211f","tid":156322,"uid":19065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"究竟係咩精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日覺得人地好討厭自己"},{"pid":"4213dcb05a2f153226863827a566629c223edd51","tid":156322,"uid":10821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:23:02.000Z","msg":"我都係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d1b2f15aba3eb88490a2cf6c38c139a1ad6038","tid":156322,"uid":47613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"我都會有種感覺，成日都諗其實其他人對我係有咩感覺係咪覺得我好煩，翻到屋企又諗老豆會唔會已經當生小一個，同屋企人完全無溝通無交流。"},{"pid":"38413a3e09381412428e11cc3614c449206769b1","tid":156322,"uid":33898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"我明 會控制唔到自己諗負面野<br />\n無時無刻都覺得自己行為舉止會得罪人<br />\n會每日都諗自己對人有咩做得唔夠好<br />\n可能因為由細到大都好介意其他人點睇自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79f8a7d9fb86e862d4a3b51c4fe9b02b254faf0","tid":156322,"uid":8243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又好矛盾咁知道所有野都係自己亂諗 其他人根本唔係咁諗<br />\n但就係控制唔到自己覺得所有人都討厭自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0188461da22e5cea469a5bfead59099ffc7f933","tid":156322,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"同人熟到咁上下就會憎人地/覺得人地憎自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後慢慢唔聯絡，再識新友朋友咁loop 落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},